quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  26,207,"Kalibakhonya shina amalayi kabamenyibwamo?"
  26,208,"Ne sikhwasishia olukongo lwosilwosi tawe nikhushili okhurumamwo Abekanyilisi."
  26,209,"(Kho bibe) obwitsulisio, ne shikhwali abakhola obubii tawe."
  26,210,"Ne Amashetani shikekha nayo tawe."
  26,211,"Ne shikakhoyeshele tawe, ne shikakhanyala tawe."
  26,212,"Toto abo bekalilwa okhuwulila."
  26,213,"Kho olalaama halala nende Nyasaye abanyasaye bandi tawe, wakhetsa waba mubalia balinyoola eshinyasio."
  26,214,"Ne wikanyilisie Abandu bobo ba ahambi."
  26,215,"Ne ore hasi olubaha lulwo khu ulia ukhuloonda mubasuubili."
  26,216,"Ne nibalakhuwulila tawe, boola mbu: “Esie ndiira ehale muno nende akamukholanga.”"
  26,217,"Ne wisiche ulia owa Amaani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,218,"Ulia ukhulolanga olwa wemanga."
  26,219,"Nende okhukalukhana khukhwo mubasujudanga."
  26,220,"Toto Ye niye Omuwulili po, Omumanyi muno."
  26,221,"Koo, ebaboolelekhwo ni wina wamashetani keshelangakhwo?"
  26,222,"Keshelanga buli omuchishi omukhongo, omunji wetsimbi."
  26,223,"Kabayililanga kalia akakaulilanga, ne abaanji mubo nababeyi."
  26,224,"Ne abembanga amashairi nibo ababakori balondangakhwo."
  26,225,"Koo, shololanga mbu bo bayiyayiyanga buli mwitwoma tawe?"
  26,226,"Ne mbu bo baboolanga akabalakholanga tawe?"
  26,227,"Halali balia basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, mana nibetsulila Nyasaye muno, mana nibashila olunyuma lwa okhukholelwa obubii. Ne balia abakholanga obubii bakhamanye mbu ni omukalukho kuli kurie kwabalikalukha."